The dr.pepper was absolutely horrible. We made her take it back. We then ask for a root beer. The waitress was not sure if she can get us a that drink. She did bring us back glass bottle root beers from the bar. We go to order our food the advertised item I wanted the waitress said they did not have it. The waitress was very in unknowledgeable about the menu.  We waited a very long time for our food to arrive. Two of the our plates where cold. Also everyone received their food but me and I had to wait even longer. As we got the bill and finished our food we realized we where charged an extra 10 just for the root beer. The waitress did not tell us about this charge. A little while later a man came up to us asking if everything was okay. We explained all of our problems he told us there was nothing he could do we should have told him sooner. We where not able to tell him sooner he didn’t approach us until after we where done.
